    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>308328</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_030_060_017&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>冗談！　ジョークだってば！
も～</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>It was just a little prank! Hold your horses! Man! </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>308440</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_030_060_018&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>街荒らしたり、
魔術暴走させたりして、
ジョークですむかよ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>We're trying to stop magic from going out of control 
and destroying everything! This is FAR from a joke! </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>308660</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_030_060_019&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>待ってよ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Wait just a second! </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>308660</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_030_060_020&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>そりゃ、イタズラしてたけど、
そーんなひどいこと
してないつもりだよ？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I know I was playing a prank and that it 
was lame but it wasn't my intention, ok? </EnglishText>
      <Notes>Maybe 
"I was just messing around you know. It was a little lame but I didn't mean anything by it, ok?"</Notes>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Problematic</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>308660</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_030_060_021&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>それに、
その魔術の暴走なんて
知らないよ？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>And what do you mean by magic going out of control? </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <BubbleId>2</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>308768</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_030_060_022&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>じゃあ、
ブライトローズさんの
しわざじゃないんですか？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>So, you aren't Miss Bright Rose? </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>308892</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_030_060_023&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>明るい薔薇色（ブライトローズ）？
あたしの名前は
&lt;Arche&gt;・クライン</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Bright Rose? My name is &lt;Arche&gt; Klein. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>10</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>308964</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_030_060_024&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;Arche&gt;……って……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>&lt;Arche&gt;...you say... </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>11</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>309072</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_030_060_025&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>えーっ！　もしかして……
ダオスを倒したっていう……？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Wait what!? Could it be...that you are
THE &lt;Arche&gt; that defeated Dhaos...? </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>12</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>309176</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_030_060_026&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>そうそう……あれ？
あたしってば、
けっこう有名人？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>You got that right! Oh, no! Did little old
me get popular all of a sudden? </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>13</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>309240</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_030_060_027&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>えっと……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Um, hey... </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>14</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>309300</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_030_060_028&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>誰……？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Who IS she...? </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>15</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>309408</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_030_060_029&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>５０年前、魔王ダオスを
倒した英雄、時空戦士の
ひとりだよ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>She's the last of the Eternal Heroes who defeated
the Demon Lord Dhaos 50 years ago!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>16</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>309508</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_030_060_030&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>５０年前？
でも、そんな歳には
見えないけど……？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>50 years ago? She doesn't look that old to me... </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>17</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>309608</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_030_060_031&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>あたし、これでもいちおー、
ハーフエルフだかんね</JapaneseText>
