      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>28</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>311048</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_030_060_048&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ま、でも餅は餅屋って言うしぃ、
&lt;Klarth&gt;に聞いてくれば？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>You know what they say, one should talk to the specialist 
